Package: clinicalTrialSimulator
Type: Package
Title: Clinical Trial Data Simulation in CDISC-Compatible Format
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jorge", "Alcántara", email = "jorge.alcantara.espinosa@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Simulates realistic clinical trial datasets for Phases I–III, including patient demographics,
    treatment allocation, time-to-event outcomes, dropout (with adverse event logic), and longitudinal data.
    Outputs are compatible with CDISC ADaM standards and include support for multilevel trial structures 
    such as countries and sites. Designed for SAP prototyping and simulation-based analysis workflows.
